Miracle Godson drowned after jumping into deep waters at East Quarry near Wigan on Friday . 
  His lifeless body was found by police divers at about 5pm on the hottest day of the year . 
  Police say his death is not being treated as suspicious but an inquest will be held . 
  Miracle was reported missing after he jumped into deep water and failed to surface . 
  He was tipped for rugby league stardom and played for Wigan St Judes . 
 